india-energy-atlas
Copyright 2026 India Energy Atlas (energymap.in)

This product includes software developed at India Energy Atlas
(https://energymap.in/).

This is the consumer Python SDK for the Atlas data platform served
at api.energymap.in. It is the Python counterpart to the auto-
generated TypeScript SDK published at @saral-systems/ies-client.

Sister repositories:
  - https://github.com/India-Energy-Atlas/ies-ingest
    Orchestration / contract layer for IES-shaped state-demand
    ingestion. Run inside a pilot stack; this SDK consumes APIs
    that such pilots may publish.

Positioning: this repository is offered under Apache 2.0 as a
consumer client for the Atlas API. The Atlas data platform is
"IES-shaped" — produced against IES Architecture v0.4 (Ministry
of Power, 27 Mar 2026) — but is NOT certified IES-compliant.
The India Energy Stack programme is owned by the Ministry of
Power; this SDK does not speak for IES, certify against IES,
or act as a reference implementation of the IES specification.

